---
title: Sweet Hoisin-Glazed Meatballs with Roasted Sweet Potato and Broccolini
description: We’re big fans of baking, rather than frying, our meatballs for a healthier alternative to this dinnertime staple. But don’t worry, the dish is still jam-packed with flavour thanks to a sweet hoisin glaze, roasted sweet potatoes, and crispy veggies. One bite and you’ll be hooked.
